        "`goseg/startram/startram.go` (~900 lines) combines HTTP client operations (`FetchRegions`, `Register`, `GetBackup`), config persistence side effects (`config.UpdateConf`, `config.StartramConfig`), event publication (`EventBus <- ...`), and backup restore internals (`writeBackupToVolume`, archive extraction, docker inspect command execution).",
